description: Try our easy to follow Baked Fish & Chips recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Baked Fish & Chips Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Meanwhile, whisk eggs in a shallow bowl. Combine crushed chips and parmesan in a separate bowl. Dip the fish pieces into egg then coat with chip mixture, pressing on them firmly. Lay on a lined tray and bake for 10 minutes or until golden and cooked through. Serve fish strips with cooked chips, salad, lemon wedges and aioli.
